<title>In a First-Class Cabin</title>

<line>
Kazuma:
Who's there? <textEffects>(Who could it be at this hour?)</textEffects>
</line><line>???:
...<textEffects>A detective</textEffects>.
</line><line>Kazuma:
'A detective'? Who?
</line><line>???:
...<textEffects>A great detective</textEffects>.
</line><line>Kazuma:
<textEffects>(...I don't get it. What's a great detective-)</textEffects>
</line><line>???:
