</line><line>Kazuma:
<textEffects>(<span style="color:#E16935">Inconvenience me</textEffects>? Well... I'd be lying if I said no. After all... ...there's <textEffects>a stowaway</textEffects> in that wardrobe right over there!)</span> It's just me in here, you see. No one else. So you might perhaps want to focus your attention on one of the other first-class cabins.
</line><line>???:
