</line><line>Kazuma:
...! <textEffects>(This is going to be a tough one to argue...)</textEffects>
</line><line>???:
I was watching you quite intently, sir. And I assure you I saw no signs of a sneeze.
</line><line>Kazuma:
<textEffects>(Argh! Couldn't Ryunosuke have held his nose?!)</textEffects>
</line><line>???:
...As I was saying, I shall need to examine this <textEffects>wardrobe</textEffects>.
</line><line>Kazuma:
<textEffects>(We've had it now then. The game's up...)</textEffects>
</line>
<center>*Click creeeeeeak*
<line>.........
.........
</line>
.........</center>
<line>
???:
